metadata.name: Rekt Garage Entrance Ticket #0001
metadata.description: Rekt Garage A is a community-driven incubator & launchpad of their own degen PFP collections. 10,000 Entrance Tickets to access all Garage lab's actions. Each ticket grants perks, including the following: - Whitelist spots for all upcoming collections from the Garage lab; - Royalty share from launches; - Voting on ideas and direction; - NFT minting & trading tools, that is already used by the team; - Premium features on Garage's multi-function NFT platform currently under development; - A few other cool things as the project moves forward. For more details, visit our website https://rektgarage.xyz/
